definitions.definition: Any Arctic and subarctic - dwelling deer of the species Rangifer tarandus , with a number of subspecies .
examples: Santa Claus' sleigh is supposedly pulled by eight reindeer

definitions.definition: Any species, subspecies, ecotype , or other scientific grouping of such animals.

main_definition: ( plural: reindeer ) Any Arctic and subarctic - dwelling deer of the species Rangifer tarandus , with a number of subspecies .
secondary_definitions: ( plural: reindeers , biology ) Any species, subspecies, ecotype , or other scientific grouping of such animals.
